    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.SuccessToken">SuccessToken</PageRef> ->
    ConversionBool
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ConversionBool</TypeRef> method implicitly converts this type to bool, marking the value as read.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[operator bool() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        True if the token represents success, false if it represents failure.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
